---
title: Tex-Mex Turkey Burgers with Chipotle-Ranch Salad
description: On the hunt for a flavourful turkey burger? Look no further! This tasty turkey burger is spiced with our Southwest spice blend and slathered with guacamole and ranch dressing. There will be no boring salad tonight either! We've dressed carrots, cucumbers and spring mix with a zippy chipotle-ranch dressing.  Your taste buds won't know what hit them!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-dinde-facon-tex-mex-6997d63b.jpg
